Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.76,0:00:07.20,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,No Money!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:11.46,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,Living your life is a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:15.83,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,But one step ahead,\NI hear there's only darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:18.98,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,Art is long. Life is short.
