Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:31.15,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't want\Nregrets in your youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:34.50,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,I can be your ultimate weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:37.59,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,So come on... Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:40.86,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hesitate...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:47.13,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,...over holding this hand of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:55.11,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is\Na special God-given chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:01:00.62,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,It's romance for sure.\NWe're sexy men for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:04.49,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,If you dare to dream, it will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:07.39,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,After this great love of ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:11.83,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm taking you along for the ride.
