Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:11.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our next product is of mixed blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:16.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a college student\Nand somewhat older...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:21.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...but look at his finely textured skin.\NHis soft chestnut-colored hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:26.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the fine features of his face.\NIt's rare to see this level of quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:31.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Needless to say, he has never been\Ntaken from behind. Nor frontally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:36.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The lucky winner of the bid should\Nfeel free to examine him personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:39.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we start at 50 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:40.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,55!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:41.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,60!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:42.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,65!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:43.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,70!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:45.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,70!\N75!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,80!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,85!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:53.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,100!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:56.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've just heard 100 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:59.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other bids?\NIs that the final bid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:03.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then for 100 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then for 100 million...\N120 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,120 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,All in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:22.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice of his...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:48.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That hand of his...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:02.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, I'll lend you my...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:09.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How he rescued me\Nfrom the depths of despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:43.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where am l?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:50.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:54.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bastards... Pumping you\Nfull of those damned drugs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I call a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:59.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:00.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:04.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you apologizing for?\NI'll get you something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:06.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:11.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:15.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.\NI just wanted to thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:23.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... you saved me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:25.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:30.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to thank you...\NAfter you've been so kind to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:34.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So good to a stranger like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:39.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on... What did he say just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:41.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stranger?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:43.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You mean you don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:47.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was shoved into\Na car all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:52.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, if you move...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:03.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:07.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like I said, you've still\Ngot drugs in your system!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:09.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:14.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, Tetsuo...\Nmy cousin was there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:18.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They might still be holding\Nhim captive in that restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:21.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:25.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should remember the guy\Nright in front of you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Tetsuo lshii, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:32.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:36.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you're a friend of Tetsuo's?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:38.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:41.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:45.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a loan shark,\Nand lshii is one of my clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:48.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He pinched about\Nthree million and ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pinched?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:52.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He borrowed money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:53.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Debt Report (individual)\NBut...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:55.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Debt Report (individual)\NFrom this Axi place too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He borrowed all these millions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be a yakuza-run casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:05.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,As an amateur, he must've gotten\Ncarried away and gotten scammed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:10.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were auctioned off by Axi\Nas collateral for lshii's debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Tetsuo also...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:17.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No one in the universe\Nis eccentric enough to take him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:22.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a guy like that... It's not like\Nhe doesn't have viable body parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:26.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Liver... kidneys... corneas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you sold them piecemeal,\Nyou'd make some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:33.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to go save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:36.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:40.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it? Ishii sold\Nyou off to save his own skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:44.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd never do that... We're cousins...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:47.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what? There are countless\Npeople who'd sell off their relatives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:49.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:53.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from lshii.\NYou'll just get hurt if you get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:55.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you this for your own good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:59.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But Tetsuo is my only...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuo, Tetsuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:08.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can deny it, but you can't ignore\Nthe fact lshii doesn't care about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:09.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:12.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Face up to it!\NYou were used and betrayed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:16.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That it'd be better\Nfor you if that bastard died!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:28.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:35.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You don't know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:38.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with you...\NYou're just a stranger...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to do with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stranger...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:02.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I have a stronger bond\Nthan blood between us, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:04.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:07.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't get\Nthe position you're in, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:12.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:15.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know what\Nyour intended purpose was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:18.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...and who became your owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:22.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-intended purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:26.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't move around much\Ntill the drugs wear off anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:29.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You might as well enjoy yourself too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me teach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:37.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This time around,\Nso you won't forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:41.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:47.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're a virgin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I'm being gentle, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:53.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to get you conditioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:03.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want\Nto feel any pain, just lie there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:18.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:20.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:24.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both men...\NHow can we? It's not right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:28.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Abnormal, you mean?\NWho are you to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:32.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A man's hand is lifting you\Nup from behind like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:39.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving you another erection right\Naway... What does that make you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:42.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just let you come orally too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:45.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:54.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Men doing men... abnormal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:56.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me. I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:11:00.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I made love\Nto you in my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:03.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...I thought the same thing\Nmyself over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:05.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But none of that really matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Abnormal or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...I want you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:22.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:55.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were\Ngoing to cherish him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:01.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that he'd never get hurt.\NI'd protect him myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet look at what I'm doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:12.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I really want...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:37.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... I beg of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:40.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:44.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to go or Tetsuo will... Tetsuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:50.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be happy to set you free.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,On condition that\Nmy money is returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:57.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The money lshii borrowed\Nand the money paid for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:59.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 200 million including expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:02.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I'll let you shoulder it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:07.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Until it's paid in full, you belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:09.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be free, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:11.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:15.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's forgotten and rejected you,\Nbut you'll still struggle for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:20.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But 200 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:24.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. I'll let you earn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:29.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... If it means I can make\Nyou mine, I'll just bind you to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:32.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's by money or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:37.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I'll buy that body of\Nyours for 500,000 yen each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:48.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he'll use\Nhis house as collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:53.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The land isn't bad,\Nbut the registry is highly questionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:56.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not worth discussing.\NAny other way of collecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:14:00.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there's some real\Nestate in Kamakura as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:03.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... It's left such a bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:06.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ayase's to blame too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:09.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Trusting a scumbag like Tetsuo\Njust because they're cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:16.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it we should deny him more\Nfunds and try to collect the total soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:23.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! Miss Kaoruko\Nhas come to pay her debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:26.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing besides\Nthe land in Kamakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:30.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There is, but that's the only thing\Nwe can wring money out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:31.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The factory...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:35.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why are you\Nignoring me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:39.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you treat childhood\Nfriends? I mean I'm a client!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:42.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy transvestites\Nshouldn't act like clients!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:48.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy? If you can't see my beauty,\Nrun to the eye doctor right this second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:52.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You run to a shrink!\NAnyway, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me. I tried to stop her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:59.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Ms. Someya insisted on\Nmeeting with you face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:02.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuba, no sugar in my coffee, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:07.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I've been ordered not\Nto serve you anything but salt water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:13.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come to think of it,\Nyou two are related, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:21.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hypothetically, let's say one of you\Nwas actually an evil bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:24.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...and was feeding off the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:27.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said hypothetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:32.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim hasn't realized he's being\Nscammed, and out of kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:35.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...I expose the evil brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:40.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So between the scumbag relative\Nand the well-meaning stranger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...which would you trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:46.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well-meaning? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:51.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I answer someone who\Nlooks like he just killed 2 or 3 people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:55.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true in\Nthis line of business...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:59.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's not uncommon\Nto see family quarrels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:03.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's often because they're\Nrelated that their hatred grows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's human nature...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:11.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...to tend to believe in your\Nrelatives even if you're aware of that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:12.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who's never\Nimpressed by anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:20.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who has\Nno compassion for his kin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:24.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who's merciless\Nto traitors, family or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(419,383)}"Human empathy" means nothing to them
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:34.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuba, collect that tranny's\Nmoney and get her out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:38.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And about that loan... Give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:43.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But make him bring his daughter\Non board as a co-signer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:46.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since ultimately,\Nwe can make money off women.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:49.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,His company won't\Nlast another two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:52.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cover him and set\Nhim up for the right time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:54.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...and clean him out for all he's got.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:57.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If he refuses, tell him\Nwe're collecting in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:16:58.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:13.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanoh's not himself.\NIt's just women's intuition, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:17.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see a woman\Nanywhere in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because normally, he's more...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:23.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no vulnerabilities,\Nand he's hard to approach, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:25.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kanoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:28.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,His work's as flawless as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:32.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But he does seem somewhat\Ndistracted in the office...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:35.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, did you see\Nthat scar by his eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:38.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That man's like\Na walking lethal weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world did that to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:45.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, even\Nhis visualizations were true to form.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:48.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're dumped in\NTokyo Bay, I won't rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:57.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I've got to create an\Nenvironment conducive to calm talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:02.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you do,\Ntry not to scare him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:05.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Approach him in a gentle manner...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:11.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, I'm starting\Nto feel like I'm taming a wild animal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a chipmunk or\Na flying squirrel, a small creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:31.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you well enough to be up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:39.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...\NCareful! Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:40.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful! Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:43.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you cut\Nyourself somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:50.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even bear to be touched?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:59.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... I'll clean it up right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:02.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No sense in talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:08.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's come to this, then taking\Nhim by force is the only way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:14.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No good... Then it'll be\Nthe same as last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:22.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Let me take a look.\NWe've got to take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! You've got a high fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:41.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you walking\Naround for? Stay in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:42.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:48.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get something to reduce\Nthat fever. Lie there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:49.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:01.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:08.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I never take medicine myself, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, you don't\Nhave to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:15.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to getting fevers like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:17.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:19.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Queer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:23.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy right now!\NWhen will you ever get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:27.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me like this again and I'll peel\Nyour skin off, you damn queer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:31.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I found it, Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:47.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am l, an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:52.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I could've saved time by sending out\Nfor medicine instead of looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:54.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,One pill per dose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:57.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's\Nthe matter with me, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:04.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:07.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do as I say. Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:25.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:30.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It says you shouldn't take\Nthis on an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:33.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't eaten anything\Nsince yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:35.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,At least take a bite...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like he'd eat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:42.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't have to force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:43.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:48.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:50.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been on my own awhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:54.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So having someone take care\Nof me like this when I'm sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.51,0:21:56.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:02.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time\Never for me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:04.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking care of someone like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:14.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but that stuff is supposed\Nto be for human consumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:16.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing toxic either...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:18.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.78,0:22:31.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:35.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was freaked out\Nand wary, but now all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:38.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a weird kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.55,0:22:43.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, I guess\NI must be pretty weird myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:48.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting nervous that I'm saying the\Nwrong thing and getting carried away...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.35,0:23:42.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to the office for now.\NGet some rest, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:44.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:45.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.35,0:23:48.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.29,0:23:51.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That scar by your eye. I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:23:57.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.63,0:23:59.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.47,0:24:04.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.74,0:24:06.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.57,0:24:07.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishii!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.78,0:24:10.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishii?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:15.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuo! Is that Tetsuo?\NPlease let me talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.22,0:24:18.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Better not.\NHe won't give you good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.66,0:24:22.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.86,0:24:24.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yukiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.49,0:24:26.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuo... Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.83,0:24:30.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! They still have me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.16,0:24:32.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They might be planning to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.27,0:24:36.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.54,0:24:41.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If your life can restore our\Nstolen money, it's a small price to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.21,0:24:44.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure they waste you\Nin a way that'll be profitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.98,0:24:46.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.91,0:24:51.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that though, let me talk\Nto him. He's there, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.55,0:24:55.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you\Ncould've found out this number.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.96,0:25:00.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.04,0:25:15.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you still trust that lshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.54,0:25:16.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.01,0:25:21.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were you, would you lure\Nyour loved ones back into danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.98,0:25:27.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is I did think something\Nwas wrong more than once...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.99,0:25:34.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this time around, I did\Nsuspect that I was being deceived...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.79,0:25:39.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no other family\Nbesides the lshii family...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.00,0:25:43.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I couldn't believe Tetsuo would...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.90,0:25:46.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't want to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.18,0:25:53.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Believing in your\Nrelatives is human nature...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.51,0:25:55.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.15,0:25:58.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase wants to believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.82,0:26:02.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,By calling someone his relative...\NHe's trying to cling to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.06,0:26:11.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.97,0:26:14.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Admitting that you're all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.40,0:26:20.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still want to see lshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.07,0:26:23.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.68,0:26:28.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.85,0:26:29.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.85,0:26:35.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were lshii, I'd never\Nleave him on his own...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.36,0:26:41.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ayase needs\Nsomeone right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.50,0:26:45.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it isn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.74,0:26:52.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.34,0:26:53.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.35,0:27:02.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.18,0:27:04.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.\NO-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.62,0:27:06.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The president...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.15,0:27:08.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...is getting the door for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.69,0:27:09.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.49,0:27:13.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.30,0:27:25.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, are you really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.47,0:27:30.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that casino's people won't\Nlet him get away unscathed this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.88,0:27:33.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.18,0:27:36.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.79,0:27:45.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll send him to a place where\Nhe has no one to rely on but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.77,0:27:59.17,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,When I opened\Nthe window and spoke to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.27,0:28:05.44,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...I could see that the wintry\Nnight sky was sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.78,0:28:11.48,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the emotions\Nof all the people everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.58,0:28:17.52,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...had turned into those stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.26,0:28:25.20,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,That promise we made so long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.50,0:28:30.66,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...is something I still\Ncling tightly to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.77,0:28:39.15,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,On sleepless nights in my dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.15,0:28:49.11,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if a single tear falls...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.22,0:28:55.13,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll never forget that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.43,0:29:07.03,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved,\Njust keep me warm forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.71,0:29:13.37,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm caught in a rainfall of grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.48,0:29:21.01,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...I want to become your love.
